{"tid":1034971,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"殷商人算唔算係中國人？","createTime":"2019-02-24T10:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T08:06:18.000Z","uid":152313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1b8101af9fa7c9ee1fad5b377cf9f24aa675897c","tid":1034971,"uid":152313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"唔知大家知唔知呢單料：<br />\n<br />\n日前，「曾多年擔任中國社科院考古研究所安陽殷墟考古隊隊長」的唐際根教授，終於透露他在1996年，曾安排加拿大 Lakehead University 的分子生物學和古人類研究的學者 El Moto 到安陽工作站，選取「黑河路」的殷商人骨標本，預備稍後合作檢測殷商人的遺傳基因，但在簽約前一刻，應中國科學院基因研究所的基因學家W和J要求，把該標本交了給她們。其後得出的檢測結果令人極之震撼 &mdash;&mdash; <strong>殷商人的基因屬西亞人種，而此結果與之前日本學者所做的吻合</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2019/02/the-myth-of-5000-years-of-history/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2019%2F02%2Fthe-myth-of-5000-years-of-history%2F&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xcF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=67d266b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2019/02/the-myth-of-5000-years-of-history/</a>"},{"pid":"120d8c3fe4330ef74de6fff7fd40ab6c01416b4e","tid":1034971,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"唔合理<br />\n因為依加嘅大陸人都係中亞、美索不達米亞嚟"},{"pid":"806c986bfcd3d43aa1804a028ee8e22067d902c8","tid":1034971,"uid":9053,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"姐係妲己鬼妹樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db40bbcb33e7509dd75f4139c4376b29af81891e","tid":1034971,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"韓國人"},{"pid":"35fbc8af0c592e4c7ed3feb8a9c0c6810aaf66e8","tid":1034971,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"西亞即係閃米特定波斯人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f207422d73c3088c7ddbe7b807051b3a8feaa6c3","tid":1034971,"uid":44391,"like":0,"dislike":0,